# Control property for the Arc-2 data worker. The login daemon (u:r:diaspore:s0) starts the su:s0
# worker via `setprop ctl.start diaspore_roamd`. Give THIS service's control property its own label
# (more specific than the generic `ctl.start$` fallback) so the daemon can be granted `set` on just
# this one service, not arbitrary `ctl.start`. See diaspore.te (ctl_diaspore_roamd_prop + set_prop).
ctl.start$diaspore_roamd        u:object_r:ctl_diaspore_roamd_prop:s0
# Control property for the on-demand OTA updater (DIA-20260618-03): the daemon ctl.starts it on a
# user-confirmed install (see diaspore.te ctl_diaspore_otad_prop + set_prop).
ctl.start$diaspore_otad         u:object_r:ctl_diaspore_otad_prop:s0
